column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMag_i, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN Galaxy p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
